Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), autotools-dev, libiw-dev, libglib2.0-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: lxnm
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, net-tools, wpasupplicant, wireless-tools, dhcp3-client 
Description: Lightweight X11 Network Manager
 LXNM(Lightweight X11 Network Manager) is a lite network manager daemon 
 attempts to make networking configuration and setup as painless and 
 automatic as possible.
 .
 LXNM is default Network Manager for LXDE(the Lightweight X11 Desktop
 Environment) project.
